{"tid":1393231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［遍地開花］樹藝及園藝界匿名公開信","createTime":"2019-08-01T04:25:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T19:02:10.000Z","uid":237568,"like":124,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"bf70bfb5c6c889881c38b063e8d3527b8e793676","tid":1393231,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:25:20.000Z","msg":"大家可能對呢個界別唔係咁熟悉<br />\n呢個界別包括攀樹師 樹藝師 園境師 etc<br />\n一直以黎，特別係去年山竹為香港市民服務<br />\n我地遲左 對唔住<br />\n後生仔付出既已經夠多喇<br />\n今次比我地企係你地前面啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n致各位香港市民：<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群在從事樹藝及園藝界別，致力令香港成為一個和大自然調和，而非為發展無視環境的專業人員。<br />\n<br />\n自今年二月政府推出逃犯條例修訂，政府數月以來漠視主流民意，一直偏聽支持修訂聲音，以致六月期間反對條例修訂的和平示威，逐漸演變為警民衝突。<br />\n<br />\n期間政府雖以「暫緩修例」、「壽終正寢」等字眼，意圖混淆視聽欺暪香港市民，但無意全面撤回修定，而市民行使合法權力表達訴求，政府逃避正面回應，只以逐步升級的武力去壓制反對聲音，縱容警方濫用過份武力，我們表示強烈憤慨和不滿。<br />\n<br />\n至七月廿一日晚上，香港警方竟任由黑社會份子在內的白衣人，在元朗無差別攻擊市民。翌日政府高層及警方上下竟然迴避斥責白衣人暴行，並反指示威人士為暴徒，包庇元朗恐襲，執法者竟視法治於無物，如此回應令人氣憤，對此我們深表憤怒，予以強烈譴責；而市民繼續無所畏懼，積極表達訴求，其無私勇毅亦令人敬佩動容。<br />\n<br />\n就此本著專業和人類良知，我們必須指出問題根源，並要求政府高層正面回應及落實香港市民五大訴求：<br />\n<br />\n1. 來屆特首及立法會選舉中，全面落實普選<br />\n2.成立以退休法官為主席，成員由廣泛界別人士，而不限於親政府人士，各政治光譜立場之人數也須相約，確保持平之獨立調查委員會，調查由9/6/2019起，警方種種惹人疑慮，令市民不安的行動，釋除社會大眾的不安<br />\n3. 特區政府立即全面撤回逃犯條例修訂<br />\n4.政府立即收回「暴動」定性<br />\n5. 絕不追究反對逃犯條例抗爭者，停止濫捕並釋放有關人士<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油！毋忘初衷！<br />\n<br />\n一眾關心熱愛香港的樹藝及園藝同業上<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pWiH6pj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpWiH6pj.png&h=bba01d40&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ixriEKk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FixriEKk.png&h=a0623943&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w0GFS4m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw0GFS4m.png&h=b0eedc40&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z6oEpa2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ6oEpa2.png&h=fde39d99&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GqDhaQ3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGqDhaQ3.png&h=e209d1e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eHCJQQ4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeHCJQQ4.png&h=86b1deeb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iq8dtCM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiq8dtCM.png&h=35c701f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JCX54a7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJCX54a7.png&h=7da84aa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gkCmCwe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgkCmCwe.png&h=8df0fe8d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aDxE8CV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaDxE8CV.png&h=ceee6c4c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/myDdtCX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmyDdtCX.png&h=6373aebe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2cOwZKE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2cOwZKE.png&h=d7c0a26c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tyv7x4F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTyv7x4F.png&h=98726b7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfb434e4f04e45fdf4f2267ae55a6a7fa28c95ac","tid":1393231,"uid":237568,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:26:59.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會罷工"},{"pid":"ad267bd8878e08ab14dc2216403e85e0672ca941","tid":1393231,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:27:13.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會罷工"},{"pid":"30d2bb938678309a9616800fa5d082af993e528b","tid":1393231,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:27:28.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會罷工"},{"pid":"77fb06e97de41c3d6bfabfb4cc91634e0cc56beb","tid":1393231,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,